## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [uxt1 uxt2 uxt3]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Delayed growth, darker leaf color, shorter stems, vessels severely collapsed, thin interfascicular fiber cells, reduced secondary cell walls, reduced cell wall. Reduced Xyl, XyG, xylan, lignin content, increased Ara content (leaf, stem, anther filament). Reduced length of xylan backbone, modified xylan structure (methylation of alpha-GlcA residues). Reduced silique development and seed production, reduced anther filament length, indehiscent anthers with little pollen produced.
